Package: ndn-tools
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: Collection of tools for Named Data Networking (NDN)
 this package contains tools recommended to be installed on all NDN nodes:
  - peek: transmit a single packet between a consumer and a producer
  - chunks: segmented file transfer between a consumer and producer
  - ping: test reachability between two nodes
  - dump: analyze traffic on wire
  - dissect: inspect TLV structure of NDN packet format
  - dissect-wireshark: Wireshark extension to inspect TLV structure of NDN
         packets
  - pib: a service to manage the public information of keys and publish
         certificates
